Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫“来玩吧”？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快干掉他！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲虫兽 进化吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲虫兽 进化！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚古兽 进化！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暴龙兽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比多兽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙好菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它进化了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 它和我们一样是成熟期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样？竟然一点效果也没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比多兽！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暴龙兽！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太一 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是完全体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它进化了两次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也进化到完全体！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在进化时攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？亚古兽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲虫兽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…耍诈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得让甲虫兽它们休息休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！在进化时偷袭 真卑鄙！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太一 有一封澳大利亚男孩寄来的邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:33.71,Draw,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HDDDDDD}{\a5}{\pos(379,150)}{\p1}m 0 0 l 263 0 263 14 0 14 m 0 28 l 101 28 101 40 0 40 m 200 86 l 227 86 227 98 200 98{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:33.71,Interface,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(380,150)}{\fs14}你好,刚才的生物叫数码兽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:33.71,Interface,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(380,178)}{\fs14}真是新鲜呢。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:33.71,Interface,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(582,234)}{\fs14}汤姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:39.45,Draw,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HDDDDDD}{\a5}{\pos(391,175)}{\p1}m 0 0 l 119 0 119 14 0 14{\p0}
