Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:39.45,Interface,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(391,232)}{\fs14}难道你们真的那么菜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:39.45,Draw,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HDDDDDD}{\a5}{\pos(501,262)}{\p1}m 0 0 l 48 0 48 14 0 14{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:39.45,Interface,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\pos(501,262)}{\fs14}简
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我第一次看见数码兽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看到了刚才那场战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是从新加坡来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个打一个都输 它们那么菜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有从那个水母发的邮件
